      "name": "Note: When Chat Message Received"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Classify with AI\n\nLLM classification into: Question, Complaint, Feedback (+fallback). Output port order matches this list.\n\nPorts: ①→ Store as Question · ②→ Store as Complaint, Capture Failure Context · ③→ Store as Feedback · ④→ Alert Slack — Other\n\n⚠ failures exit via the error rail",
        "width": 280,
        "height": 232,
        "color": 6
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
