      "id": "3fa0c6b4-f24a-3081-8528-27e130f98b6e",
      "name": "Note: Classify with AI"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### OpenRouter Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Classify with AI** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 OpenRouter API key",
        "width": 280,
